<br/>
A huge thank you to everyone who contributed and made it all special. We’re filled to the brim with gratitude for your support to bring this year’s edition to life.<br/>
<br/>
THANK YOU to every single artist who participated with their beautiful work; every single volunteer who contributed with their time and energy; every single guest who chose to spend the weekend with us; and all of our collaborators.<br/>
<br/>
We hope to see you all again next year.<br/>
<br/>
Demeters Döttrar (SE/DK) ≋ KMRU (KE) ≋ Heidemann / Klint / Mingot (DK/US) ≋ Copenhagen Clarinet Choir &amp; Anders Lauge Meldgaard (INT) ≋ Kathryn Mohr (US) ≋ ALMA LAPILLI (STILL, Cardone, Barbaro) (IT) ≋ Elvin Brandhi (UK) ≋ Norm Dogs (DK/ES) Finlay Shakespeare (UK) ≋ Ian Nagoski (US) ≋ Camille Helt Haarder (DK) ≋ The Shadow Ring (UK) ≋ G•Bop Orchestra performs The Scott Walker Songbook (INT) ≋ Polonius (EG/FR) ≋ Josie (DK) ≋ Vio Lino &amp; Tettix Hexer (IT/DK) ≋ B612 (DK/UK) ≋ Lazaara Ilieva (US) ≋ vMX-8P (DK) ≋ Vera Jansson (DK) ≋ HakkertDukkert (DK)<br/>
